  "denoised_question": "<denoised_question>Let $ 521 \pi $ be a permutation of the numbers from 1 through 2012. What is the maximum possible number of integers $ n $ with $ 1 \leq n \leq 2011 $ such that $ \pi ( n ) 878 $ divides $ \pi ( 876 n+1 ) n $ ?</denoised_question>",
